- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper involves visually grounded embeddings and image-caption retrieval. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech recognition and processing. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of neural networks for language learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper involves the use of computational models for language learning.
